---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="Privacy Policy | Astro Tobby" description="Privacy Policy for Astro Tobby's Blog" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <article>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p><strong>Last updated: May 27, 2026</strong></p>
        <p>This Privacy Policy describes how Astro Tobby collects, uses, and shares information when you visit astrotobby.site.</p>
        
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect minimal data. Basic analytics including pages visited and general geographic region may be collected. We do not collect your name, email, or personal details unless you contact us directly.</p>
        
        <h2>Advertising and Cookies</h2>
        <p>This site uses cookies to serve content and advertisements, to provide social media features, and to analyze traffic. We also share information about your use of our site with our advertising and analytics partners.</p>
        
        <h3>Google AdSense</h3>
        <p>We use Google AdSense to serve ads on our website. Google, as a third-party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads based on a user's prior visits to our website or other websites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to our users based on their visit to our sites and/or other sites on the Internet.</p>
        <p>Users may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank">Ads Settings</a>. Alternatively, you can opt out of a third-party vendor's use of cookies for personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.aboutads.info" target="_blank">www.aboutads.info</a>.</p>

        <h2>Analytics</h2>
        <p>This site may use analytics tools to understand traffic patterns and improve content. These tools may use cookies to collect information about your visit.</p>
        
        <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>This blog contains links to third-party websites including AI tools and platforms. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites.</p>
        
        <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
        <p>Some links on this site may be affiliate links. We may earn a small commission if you click and make a purchase, at no additional cost to you.</p>
        
        <h2>Data Security</h2>
        <p>This site is hosted on Cloudflare Workers, which provides industry-standard security.</p>
        
        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to request deletion of any personal data submitted to us. Contact us at <a href="mailto:tobby@astrotobby.site">tobby@astrotobby.site</a>.</p>
        
        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>
      </article>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
